description: This top 15% Cooter purrs with a rating of 64, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 128, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 2 for East, 1 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [128 Votes, Top 15%]
